Install a package with: sdgpkg install <name>
List installed packages with: sdgpkg list
Update all packages with: sdgpkg upgrade
Search available packages with: sdgpkg fetch
Check for updates with: sdgpkg upgradable
View package info with: sdgpkg info <name>
Remove a package with: sdgpkg uninstall <name>
Clone without installing with: sdgpkg sync <name>
